HEADWORD: Perisystole
<hw>Per`i*sys"to*le</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>peri-</ets> + <ets>systole</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>p⟦eacute⟧risystole</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>The
